    {
      "turn": 5,
      "message": "[GM] Departure preparations complete. Cart repaired. Hallan's leg injury slows travel speed.",
      "narrative": "The cart wheel repair was finished. Hallan limped onto the cart. Mira organized the luggage and looked at the party. \"We can leave now. About a day to Karendel... it'll be a bit slow because of father's leg.\" The road continues east along the trade route. The sun is still high.",
      "timestamp": "22:26:04",
      "archived_at": "2026-03-25"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "message": "[GM] Departure preparation. Saiki suggests to Noel to pick up items dropped on the ground. Hallan and Mira react.",
      "narrative": "Hallan turned from the cart. \"That stuff? Got trampled by wolves, so it's worthless as merchandise. Take it if you want.\" He paused, then added, \"...The actually useful stuff is already on the cart. Thanks for the help.\" Mira rummaged through her bag and pulled out a small vial, handing it to Noel. \"I brought this to treat father, but there's one left. It's a thank-you for your help.\" Noel nodded as he took the vial. Scattered on the ground were torn cloth scraps, broken pottery shards, and a few handfuls of crushed dried fruit. Hardly anything useful, but as Noel searched thoroughly, he found a coil of rope and a flint.",
      "timestamp": "22:36:53",
      "archived_at": "2026-03-25"
    },
