    {
      "turn": 22,
      "message": "[GM] Mana wire cast + night watch rotation set (1st shift Lucena, 2nd shift Noel). Camp for the night.",
      "narrative": "Saiki draped the blanket over his shoulders and said,\n\"If we want to wake up early tomorrow, we should sleep early.\"\n\nHallan cut in briefly.\n\"...We need to set a watch. There are strangers mixed in here.\"\n\nSaiki nodded, then pulled out his staff and slowly traced a circle on the ground around the camp. A thin thread of mana unwound from the tip of the staff and seeped between the blades of grass. An invisible detection line settled into place around the campsite.\n\nLucena's eyes sparkled as she asked.\n\"Oh, what's that? A trap?\"\n\n\"Mana wire. If someone crosses it, I'll sense it.\"\n\nLucena nodded, then twirled a dagger between her fingers and settled by the campfire.\n\"Alright, but we still need a watch. That hooded person earlier was really suspicious. I'm not sleepy yet, so I'll take the first shift.\"\n\nNoel replied briefly.\n\"...Second shift.\"\n\nHe glanced at Saiki and nodded once — meaning, get some good sleep.\n\nSaiki pulled the blanket over himself and lay down by the campfire. He could faintly sense the mana threads surrounding the area. Lucena added another log to the fire. Flames rose and warmed the night air.\n\nDeep in the night. An owl's cry echoed from the forest.",
      "user_input": "Cast mana wire and sleep",
